metadata.name: CYBEX #1 : OVERTHIN'KING
metadata.description:
The "Cyber Expressionism Series" is a MACHINE x HUMAN collection of artworks inspired by the Neo-Expressionism & mixed media movements.

The background is generated using AI & Code, impossible to reproduce by hand/software.

The Characters are drawn by CYBERIUM. 

The goal was to create high contrasting pieces using joyful colors, creepy characters and a dark theme.
